487
00:36:33.398 --> 00:36:34.537
Can you repeat that?

488
00:36:35.641 --> 00:36:36.918
No tests tonight.

489
00:36:37.505 --> 00:36:40.232
They were scheduled.
but they needed turbulence.

490
00:36:40.957 --> 00:36:42.303
Too smooth tonight.

491
